2014年2月4日，湯普森接替[[比爾·蓋茨|比爾·蓋茨]]成為微軟的董事長，<ref>{{cite news|title=Bill Gates steps down as chairman, will assist new CEO as 'technology advisor'|url=http://www.theverge.com/2014/2/4/5377226/bill-gates-steps-down-microsoft-chairman-named-tech-advisor|accessdate=4 February 2014|newspaper=The Verge|archive-date=2021-03-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210309024820/https://www.theverge.com/2014/2/4/5377226/bill-gates-steps-down-microsoft-chairman-named-tech-advisor|dead-url=no}} "Gates will be succeeded as chairman by John Thompson, who joined Microsoft's board in February of 2012. Thompson is currently the CEO of Virtual Instruments and previously served as CEO and chairman of Symantec."</ref>在此之前，湯普森已經擔任微軟董事會成員兩年，他說他加入董事會的是因為他已經"欽佩微軟很多，很多，很多年"。他還說他認為微軟是"我們國家裡，真正具標誌性的企業之一"。<ref>{{cite web|url= http://www.zdnet.com/meet-microsofts-new-board-chairman-john-thompson-7000025944/|title= Meet Microsoft's new board chairman John Thompson|publisher= ZDNet|date= February 4, 2014|access-date= 2014-08-06|archive-date= 2014-11-21|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20141121025333/http://www.zdnet.com/meet-microsofts-new-board-chairman-john-thompson-7000025944/|dead-url= no}}</ref>

==政治活動  ==
湯普森是[[歐巴馬|歐巴馬]]在2008年選戰中的重要支持者，<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.mercurynews.com/breakingnews/ci_11568737|accessdate=2009-01-28|title=Nomination of Symantec CEO John W. Thompson as commerce secretary near, sources say|publisher=[[San_Jose_Mercury_News|San Jose Mercury News]]|date=January 2009|archive-date=2011-06-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110604072956/http://www.mercurynews.com/breakingnews/ci_11568737|dead-url=no}}</ref> 2009年1月，新聞來源指出歐巴馬總統正考慮讓湯普森擔任商務部長的職缺<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.latimes.com/technology/la-na-commerce-secretary27-2009jan27,1,111677.story|accessdate=2009-01-28|title=Commerce secretary may hail from Silicon Valley|publisher=[[Los_Angeles_Times|Los Angeles Times]]|date=January 2009|first=Jim|last=Puzzanghera|archive-date=2009-03-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090317075218/http://www.latimes.com/technology/la-na-commerce-secretary27-2009jan27,1,111677.story|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.denverpost.com/politics/ci_11560246|accessdate=2009-01-28|title=Outgoing Symantec CEO eyed for Commerce post|publisher=[[Denver_Post|Denver Post]]|date=January 2009|archive-date=2009-02-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090201134715/http://www.denverpost.com/politics/ci_11560246|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2009/01/27/AR2009012702560.html|accessdate=2009-01-28|title=Thompson top choice for commerce secretary: sources|publisher=[[Washington_Post|Washington Post]]|date=January 2009}} {{Dead link|date=September 2010|bot=RjwilmsiBot}}</ref>最後，參議員賈德·格雷格被選中此職務<ref>{{cite news|url=http://blogs.usatoday.com/ondeadline/2009/02/obama-nominates.html|title=Obama nominates GOP senator for Commerce secretary|publisher=[[USA_Today|USA Today]]|date=January 2009|accessdate=2010-05-07|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090206144342/http://blogs.usatoday.com/ondeadline/2009/02/obama-nominates.html|archivedate=2009-02-06}} </ref>。同年2月12日星期四，格雷格撤銷了自己的任職權，湯普森再次成為潛在的候選，直到最後由[[駱家輝|駱家輝]]擔任此職。

2009年，眾議院議長[[南茜·佩洛希|南茜·佩洛希]]任命湯普森至金融危機調查委員會。

